questions.question:
Look at the program below and number the following accordingly: class declaration, opening class bracket, main method, statement, closing method bracket, closing class bracket.

public class Hello {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello");
    }
}

questions.answer:
1. class declaration -> public class Hello
2. opening class bracket -> { after the class declaration
3. main method -> public static void main(String[] args)
4. statement -> System.out.println("Hello");
5. closing method bracket -> } after the statement
6. closing class bracket -> final }

