questions.question:
Look at the program below and number the following accordingly: class declaration, main method, String declaration, statement, final closing bracket.

public class City {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String place = "Chennai";
        System.out.print(place);
    }
}

questions.answer:
1. class declaration -> public class City
2. main method -> public static void main(String[] args)
3. String declaration -> String place = "Chennai";
4. statement -> System.out.print(place);
5. final closing bracket -> last }
